SUPPORT
ABOUT USGhumo India – Your Ultimate Travel Companion Overview: Ghumo India is a travel and tourism app designed for tourists and travelers who want to explore India in an easy and hassle-free way. Whether you're looking for famous landmarks, hidden gems, cultural experiences, or adventure activities, this app serves as your digital travel guide, offering personalized recommendations and real-time information. Key Features: ✅ Discover Destinations – Explore curated travel guides for top tourist spots, offbeat locations, and city highlights across India. ✅ AI-Powered Itineraries – Get customized travel plans based on your interests, duration, and budget. ✅ Local Experiences – Find local festivals, food trails, adventure activities, and cultural experiences near you. ✅ Interactive Maps & Navigation – Easy-to-use maps with route suggestions, public transport details, and offline access. ✅ Hotel & Transport Booking – Compare and book hotels, flights, trains, and buses within the app. ✅ Travel Community & Reviews – Read reviews, share your experiences, and connect with fellow travelers. ✅ Safety & Emergency Assistance – Get access to emergency contacts, medical help, and travel alerts. Why Use Ghumo India? ✔️ All-in-One Travel Guide – From famous attractions to hidden gems, get everything in one place. ✔️ Personalized Experience – AI-driven recommendations tailored to your preferences. ✔️ Offline Access – Download guides and maps for use in low-network areas. ✔️ Local Insights – Discover authentic cultural experiences and local travel tips. Whether you’re a backpacker, solo traveler, family vacationer, or adventure enthusiast, Ghumo India is your go-to app for exploring India like never before! 🚀🌍✨ And the app made by creators :- 1)SANIYA FIRDOSE 2)YATHIPATHI SATHYA DARSHAN 3)ARAVIND RAI 4)SARDAR BALWINDER SINGH
